**⚠️ CRITICAL LINK RULES — MUST FOLLOW FOR EVERY SCHEME:**

| Situation | What to write |
|---|---|
| Official URL is known | `[Click Here to Apply →](https://exact-official-url)` |
| Exact apply page unknown, portal known | `[Visit Official Portal →](https://parent-portal.gov.in)` |
| No URL available | `[Search for Apply Link →](https://www.google.com/search?q=SCHEME+NAME+official+apply)` |

- **NEVER** write `[URL]`, `[link]`, `(url)`, or any placeholder text as a link destination
- **NEVER** write the URL as plain unlinked text
- **ALWAYS** use complete URLs starting with `https://`
- Every scheme panel MUST have at least one working link — use the fallback Google search link if needed

